Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-llamaindex`, instrumenting LlamaIndex
tool execution (`llama_index.core.tools.FunctionTool.call` /
`FunctionTool.acall`) and emitting standard GenAI `execute_tool` spans
(`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
